      <description>About Me I&amp;rsquo;m a psychologist [the researching kind]. I completed my M.A. in Experimental Psychology at California State University, Fullerton. I joined the Buss Lab and started my doctoral training in IDEP at UT Austin in Fall 2017. My general research interests revolve around evolutionary psychology and individual differences. In my spare time, I play music and do outdoorsy stuff.</description>
